<meta name="description" content="A fresh floral spray on an easel to honor the memory of a loved one.

Price includes delivery.

Available in 3 color schemes:
1. Soft + Neutral - A seasonal selection of flowers in neutral hues like 
ivory, cream, champagne + notes of muted Earth tones with touches of 
greenery + filler.

2. Signature Pastel - A seasonal selection of pastel hues, like peach, 
blush, lavender, butter yellow, pale blue + ivory with touches of greenery 
+ filler. If there is a color within this palette, you would like to 
exclude, please let us know in the checkout form.

3. Bright + Cheery - A seasonal selection of bright hues, like pink, 
purple, blue, orange + yellow with touches of greenery + filler. If there 
is a color within this palette, you would like to exclude, please let us 
know in the checkout form." />
