      data-context="{&quot;websiteId&quot;:&quot;56aa9020d51cd471ca1987f8&quot;,&quot;product&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;68112bd621231b1c05f548f4&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Signature Spray&quot;,&quot;price&quot;:{&quot;currency&quot;:&quot;USD&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:&quot;317.00&quot;},&quot;soldOut&quot;:false,&quot;onSale&quot;:false,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;&lt;p style=\&quot;white-space:pre-wrap;\&quot; data-rte-preserve-empty=\&quot;true\&quot;&gt;A fresh floral spray on an easel to honor the memory of a loved one. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Price includes delivery.&lt;\/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Available in 3 color schemes: &lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Soft + Neutral - &lt;\/strong&gt;A seasonal selection of flowers in neutral hues like ivory, cream, champagne + notes of muted Earth tones with touches of greenery + filler. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Signature Pastel - &lt;\/strong&gt;A seasonal selection of pastel hues, like peach, blush, lavender, butter yellow, pale blue + ivory with touches of greenery + filler. &lt;em&gt;If there is a color within this palette, you would like to exclude, please let us know in the checkout form.&lt;\/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Bright + Cheery - &lt;\/strong&gt;A seasonal selection of bright hues, like pink, purple, blue, orange + yellow with touches of greenery + filler. &lt;em&gt;If there is a color within this palette, you would like to exclude, please let us know in the checkout form.&lt;\/em&gt;&lt;\/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;variants&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;195fb3b8-c3f0-4e0d-a39e-c64633669ae4&quot;,&quot;sku&quot;:&quot;SQ5065628&quot;,&quot;price&quot;:{&quot;currency&quot;:&quot;USD&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:&quot;317.00&quot;},&quot;unlimited&quot;:true,&quot;qtyInStock&quot;:0,&quot;soldOut&quot;:false,&quot;scarce&quot;:false,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;Color&quot;:&quot;Soft + Neutral&quot;}},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;1e8233f3-440d-44ab-a163-0ec8ccc8a80c&quot;,&quot;sku&quot;:&quo