    <p style="white-space:pre-wrap;" data-rte-preserve-empty="true">A fresh floral spray on an easel to honor the memory of a loved one. <br><br><em>Price includes delivery.</em><br><br>Available in 3 color schemes: <br><strong>1. Soft + Neutral - </strong>A seasonal selection of flowers in neutral hues like ivory, cream, champagne + notes of muted Earth tones with touches of greenery + filler. <br><br><strong>2. Signature Pastel - </strong>A seasonal selection of pastel hues, like peach, blush, lavender, butter yellow, pale blue + ivory with touches of greenery + filler. <em>If there is a color within this palette, you would like to exclude, please let us know in the checkout form.</em><br><br><strong>3. Bright + Cheery - </strong>A seasonal selection of bright hues, like pink, purple, blue, orange + yellow with touches of greenery + filler. <em>If there is a color within this palette, you would like to exclude, please let us know in the checkout form.</em></p>
  </div>

    
    
    






